### 基础路径
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/books

### ============================================
### 查询所有书籍（分页）
GET {{baseUrl}}?page=0&size=10&sort=isbn&direction=asc

### ============================================
### 按 ISBN 查询单本书
GET {{baseUrl}}/978-7-111-12345-6

### ============================================
### 按书名查询书籍
GET {{baseUrl}}/search/by-name?name=Java编程思想

### ============================================
### 新增书籍
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isbn": "978-7-111-12345-6",
  "name": "Java编程思想",
  "author": "Bruce Eckel",
  "description": "Java经典书籍",
  "publishedDate": "2007-03-01",
  "price": 108.00,
  "inventoryQty": 50
}

### ============================================
### 更新书籍
PUT {{baseUrl}}/978-7-111-12345-6
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Java编程思想（第4版）",
  "author": "Bruce Eckel",
  "description": "Java经典书籍（更新版）",
  "publishedDate": "2007-03-01",
  "price": 128.00,
  "inventoryQty": 30
}

### ============================================
### 删除书籍
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/978-7-111-12345-6
